CONTEXT LeftResidualComposition IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT LeftResidualComposition
{+ This test verifies left residual works in composition context. +}

CLASSIFY A ISA B

RELATION r[W*B]
RELATION s[Z*B]
RELATION t[X*W]
RELATION result[X*Z]

RULE testLeftResidualComposition: result = t;(r/s)

ENDCONTEXT
